<body>
Reports an assignment operation that can be replaced by an operator assignment to make your code shorter and probably clearer.
<p>
  Example:
<pre>
<code>  x = x + 3;</code>
  <code>x = x / 3;</code>
</pre>
<p>After the quick fix is applied the result looks like:
<pre>
  <code>x += 3;</code>
  <code>x /= 3;</code>
</pre>
</body>
</html>